This product includes public administrative-boundary and OpenStreetMap-derived
snapshot data. Source attribution and snapshot metadata are preserved with the
corresponding data files and project documentation.

Optional public Sentinel-2 imagery imported by the project is discovered through
Element 84 Earth Search and read from the AWS Open Data Sentinel-2 L2A COG archive.
The generated local subset preserves the STAC item identifier, source band URLs,
SAFE product URI, processing baseline, and public-data classification. Copernicus
Sentinel data remains subject to the Copernicus Sentinel Data Legal Notice:
https://sentinels.copernicus.eu/documents/247904/690755/Sentinel_Data_Legal_Notice
